[{"id":"VR596088","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows 3 identical solid conducting spheres on insulating stands labeled Sphere X, Sphere Y, and Sphere Z. Sphere X has a charge of positive 3 Q. Sphere Y has a charge of negative 7 Q. Sphere Z is uncharged.\" height=\"102\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VR596088.g04.svg\" width=\"290\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">The figure above shows three identical solid conducting spheres on insulating stands. Spheres <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>Y</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> initially have the charges indicated. First, Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>X</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is momentarily touched to Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>Y</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and then moved far away. Next, Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>Y</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is momentarily touched to Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Z\"><math alttext=\"Z\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>Z</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>. If the final charge on Sphere <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Z\"><math alttext=\"Z\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>Z</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is zero, what was its initial charge?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR596088_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative 4 Q\"><math alttext=\"negative 4 Q\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>Q</mi></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative 2 Q\"><math alttext=\"negative 2 Q\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>Q</mi></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive 2 Q\"><math alttext=\"positive 2 Q\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>Q</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive 4 Q\"><math alttext=\"positive 4 Q\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>Q</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":2}]